# PostHog analytics (aaronroy.com) — see CLAUDE.md → Analytics
# Public project key (phc_...). Client-side/safe, but kept in env to stay out of git.
PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=
# Ingestion host. Leave blank to use the same-origin reverse proxy (/zuko, see
# vercel.json) — recommended; beats adblockers. Override only for EU/self-hosted.
PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=
